title: The Top 25 Players of the 2019-20 Season Thus Far | Group Chat
description:
We run down our lists of the 25 best NBA players so far this season, including Giannis Antetokounmpo and James Harden as solo shows, but also Anthony Davis and LeBron James as well as Kawhi Leonard and Paul George as duos in Los Angeles.

Hosts: Justin Verrier and Jonathan Tjarks
